Run app in virtual env.

step 1: create isolated py envir
  python -m venv env
  .\env\Scripts\activate
  

step 2: navigate to project and install dependancies
  pip install -r requirements.txt

step 2b: set environment variables in terminal
  set FLASK_APP=app.py
  set FLASK_ENV=development

step 3: run app
  flask run

step 4: in web browswer enter the following address:
  http://localhost:8080


// updated with newest version of GCP ------------------------------
1. activate environment:
  .\env\Scripts\activate


2. Prior to running 'main.py' must set certain environment variables run each line in terminal:
  $env:INSTANCE_CONNECTION_NAME='wired-effect-419020:us-central1:bb-app-instance'
  $env:DB_NAME='bb-app-db'
  $env:DB_USER='bb-user'
  $env:DB_PASS='abcd69'

3. run main.py:
  python main.py


